      <div class="gov-title-content">
        <h2 class="max-w-550">
          Conventional mobile architecture creates mission risk
        </h2>
        <p class="gov-description overview">
          In a conventional model, traffic exits the mobile core and moves into
          public internet transit, where visibility, route assurance, and
          security posture are harder to control. For defense, intelligence, and
          allied missions, that is not just a networking issue. It is an
          operational risk. IDSECURE is built to close that gap through secure
          delivery and intelligent orchestration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gov-content-overview">
